import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, Redirect } from "react-router-dom"
import './styles/index.scss'

// CONTAINERS
import Home from './containers/Home'

const App = () => {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Switch>
        <Route exact path='/'>
          <Home />
        </Route>
      </Switch>
    </Router>
  )
}

export default App
